{
  "comment_text": {
    "sn14.30:1.2": "Also called the “principle states” (<i lang='pi' translate='no'>mahābhūta</i>). Discussed in detail at <a href='https://suttacentral.net/mn28/en/sujato#4.1'>MN 28:4.1</a>. ",
    "sn14.30:1.4": "The properties of matter that dominate in solids, liquids, plasma, and gases. "
  },
